OL,4,Ccustody searching for answers, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe family of a homeless man who died
OL,8,Fin a police cell five years ago have
OL,9,Fsaid they are still searching for
OL,10,Fanswers at the inquest into his death.
OL,12,FSimeon Francis died in a cell at
OL,13,FTorquay Police Station on 20 May 2020
OL,14,Fafter being arrested in Exeter.
OL,16,FAt the opening of the inquest at
OL,17,FCounty Hall in Exeter, senior coroner
OL,18,FIan Arrow read out a statement from Mr
OL,19,FFrancis' sister who said she was
OL,20,F"surprised and upset" following her
OL,21,Fbrother's death in custody.
