OL,7,FShe added her family wants "answers as
OL,8,Fto how Simeon came to die".
OL,10,FThe court heard Simeon was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of being carried in a stolen
OL,12,Fvehicle in Cowley Bridge Road, Exeter,
OL,13,Fin the early hours of 20 March 2020.
OL,15,FJurors were shown video footage of the
OL,16,F35-year-old telling police he had
OL,17,Ftaken drugs and that he thought he was
OL,18,Fgoing to die.
