OL,7,FIn the video, Mr Francis can be seen
OL,8,Fsitting in the back of a police van
OL,9,Ftelling officers he needs to go to
OL,10,Fhospital as he "has a heart condition"
OL,11,Fand that he "keeps collapsing".
OL,13,FHe is also heard saying: "I've taken a
OL,14,Fload of crack and heroin.
OL,16,F"Take me to hospital, I feel like I'm
OL,17,Fgoing to die. My heart is racing. I'm
OL,18,Fpassing out. I feel like I'm having a
OL,19,Fheart attack".
